 />\n<br />\n全程得佢自己知     好合乎日本人果隻民族性"},{"pid":"b1f9d8fd32fe7a5cdf7be2c366ffd69c2b98502a","tid":163955,"uid":30058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T20:59:08.000Z","msg":"1985/3145<br />\n咁其他係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3b9dbe95b9fd66e615fa083bfa7214725096cb","tid":163955,"uid":15862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T21:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1985/3145<br />\n咁其他係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲係車廂焗暈左，咁岩我琴日係東京 係我個車廂見到個"},{"pid":"8ce2b412edf5dd2919058670d2f49f403f34e323","tid":163955,"uid":2639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T21:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知係邊到睇過 大意係指 日本人平時文化係唔好阻到人<br />\n所以自殺就想引人關注同想唔同d 所以就跳軌<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n大約明你意思<br />\n<br />\n咁點解又唔安裝幕門呢？</blockquote><br />\n有心想死 幕門有意思咩？</blockquote><br />\n幕門唔係阻你自殺 係唔好阻到列車服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有心跳軌都爬到過去啦</blockquote><br />\n整到上天花板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果從運作角度黎講，一定唔裝好過裝<br />\n幕門係一樣好易壞嘅嘢，信號系統亦要upgrade 先可以包容到幕門<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日本鐵路咁高效係因為佢地系統簡單</span>，好多嘢靠專業嘅司機去做決定<br />\n多隻香爐多隻鬼，裝左幕門相信會更加多delay <br />\n當年港鐵裝幕門嘅理由係省啲冷氣錢<i